AETHERMUD CREATOR GUIDE: QCS

QCS is the Quick Creation System: template-driven building of rooms,
NPCs, weapons, and armor under /realms/<you>/area/ without writing LPC
by hand.

All QCS verbs are used through the build command, granted by the Staff
of Creation (held in inventory; coding and admin wizards only):

  build create room <dir> <file>     build create npc <file>
  build create weapon <file>         build create armor <file>
  build modify here <prop> <value>   build modify <file> <prop> <value>
  build add exit <dir> <path>        build add <npcfile> to here
  build delete <object>              build clone <file>
  build about <file|here>            build more <file|here>

For full syntax, property lists, and examples: help build

See also: build, ed
